  <?dbhtml filename="libxfont2.html"?>

  <title>libxfont2-&libxfont2-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      libXfont2 provides various services for X servers, most notably font
      selection and rasterisation (through external libraries).
    </para>

